From bee62bea1303ba5d3995b793df333e5dc09d4e0c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: louis <louis@zml.ai>
Date: Thu, 2 Jul 2026 16:02:44 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Improve xla host scheduling in 3 patches : -
 ShouldCollectiveUseMinimalResource run once when exe is built and not at each
 layer scheduling (reduce XlaModule overhead (before first thunk)) - vector
 DeviceBufferPairs replaced with inlinedvector of size 4 (list of buffers
 implied in collective for one device so 4 must be enough) - CliqueKey
 (information for one collective) caching (reduce communication scheduling
 duration)

